PHP Application Builder

Requirements:
-------------
PHP 5.2+
PEAR installation available from include path

Required PEAR libraries:
  Console_CommandLine
  Console_Color
  VersionControl_SVN [if project is in subversion]
  VersionControl_Git [if project is in git]


Installation:
-------------
Copy the sample.config.php to config.php
Edit to point to repository of desired application.



Usage:
------

phab project:create path
Creates a new project in the given path.
Path may be relative or absolute.